Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠子它…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发出这样的光 还是第一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要做这种傻事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你在这碍手碍脚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没能把半条命还给华月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这伤势看肯定是没得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆把那孩子的身体和珠子一齐交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋 一开始就打珠子和仁的主意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道珠子在仁的身体里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道还要故意伤害仁吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟约定好的可不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏结界后 东西就应该给我不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 真是个宠孩子的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真是没想到 珠子竟然会藏在他身体里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你干的…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不马上把珠子交给那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果违背约定 那家伙一定会来复仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月说发现仁的时候 他手上捏着奇怪的珠子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是华月把珠子藏在仁的身体里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和自己的半条命一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能交给他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那家伙来了 你赢得了他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭将半条命都给了仁的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊 突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要和华月做一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将自己的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月就是因为这样才死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为人父母义不容辞的责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月可是你的父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不想用孩子的生命换取存活于世的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是…又是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 马上太阳就要落山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才珠子的光芒 一定是受了第八颗珠子的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁可能出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说仁果然是最后一颗珠子的主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你爱吃的不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直觉得 这里就是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在那里没有我的容身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是我的归属地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…为我创造这一切的华月却…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的存在 让大家都变得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也是 华月也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么当初不让我就那样死去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是华月听到你刚才说的这些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会伤心死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把结界打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算逼我们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定好了就一定要遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只能这样了 虽然并非是我的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退后 仁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个良才 我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我还是再等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火势越来越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目 仁就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我们一族的遗孤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易把你带回山里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你还是回到人类居住的地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依这个火势 不久这座山都会被烧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不能待在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只要你自信地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那里就是你的栖身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我和华月也会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 我也要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和叶月一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前总是华月华月叫个不停的你 现在居然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为在人类的地方待久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做人类的孩子 看来也不全是坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不是孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:10:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们两兄弟 最珍爱的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 孩子应该也能为父母付出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我不能把叶月一个人留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许再寻死 不许比我这个父辈早逝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了吧 华月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群鸟为什么要飞入熊熊大火中去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的主人在那 所以要保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:12:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 仁也在那里咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目 放开我 叶月他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是叶月的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你送到人类的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 我怎么能丢下叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 放开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？这个要怎么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回人类的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着我们的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:13:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一样 是天狗和人类一起孕育的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月 事情正如你所言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一族会疼爱人之子 是我族的天性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 我们终将回到人类中去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就什么都不要担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不离开这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为天狗的能力用尽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把珠子交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗之首 居然为了人类的孩子沦落至此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了珍爱的人 我可以随时放弃自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 你们快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月…华月…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你自信地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你生活的那里就是你的栖身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…栖身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会守护这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护…我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很快也会被火焰包围的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 仁一个人在努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到 他就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 庄介先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也没覆盖过这么大的范围
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨 展现你的实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把刀怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发什么呆 唤风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这个势头看来火马上就会熄灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又来了个奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1006,710)}仁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶…月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…结果我还是没能救叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什么天狗之子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…什么都…做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是好好地保护了这座山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 没能带来你想要的珠子和容器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这让人伤脑筋的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都那样警告你小心天狗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…真是漂亮的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种水好像对他来说效果不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤痕也完美地愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂也剥离得很完整
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 总算值得花了这么多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然最后的珠子到了里见手里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集八个灵魂却是宿命的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那是被诅咒的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也作为八个转生灵魂的证明的珠子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能阻止它们全部到达里见的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人…还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已经离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我赶往仁君你这里时 看到了他的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男的很像庄介先生 你们认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 说来话长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是孽缘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 跟信乃你们在一起的话就能见到那个男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他总会露面的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也和信乃一起去帝都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要给叶月报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子为父母报仇 天经地义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是叶月最后交给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃说过的珠子 难道就是指这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八颗集齐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我的珠子在影那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些珠子有什么意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后会慢慢跟你讲的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也丢了的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好保管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么跟奶奶说才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 栲婆婆的话没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道你是天狗的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.18,0:22:08.06,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}一人にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.18,0:22:08.06,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}不要让我孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:11.57,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}甘く　甘く色をとって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:11.57,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}甜美地 绽放色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:15.24,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:15.24,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要轻易离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:19.62,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君は僕の命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:19.62,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你就是我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:26.50,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どうしてねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:26.50,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:31.80,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}どうして君の願いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:31.80,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}到底是为什么 你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:37.13,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみの雨に打たれながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:37.13,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}虽被悲伤之雨淋透
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:38.89,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}咲いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:38.89,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}却依旧傲然怒放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.89,0:22:46.02,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう大事なもの傷つけたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.89,0:22:46.02,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}已经不能伤害重要之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:50.52,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その静かな笑顔を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:50.52,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只想默默守候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:54.28,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ただ守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:54.28,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你那恬静的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:58.11,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:58.11,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}伸出你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:23:01.66,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独さえ壊すほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:23:01.66,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}去打破孤寂的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:04.79,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終焉の時も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:04.79,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}直到终结之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.79,0:23:07.67,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君がいるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.79,0:23:07.67,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只要有你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:09.38,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怖くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:09.38,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我就不会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:12.75,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君は僕を照らす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:12.75,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只有你能照亮我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.75,0:23:17.84,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,900)}ただ一つの光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.75,0:23:17.84,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,900)}是我唯一的光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月 我和你确实相像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是一模一样也毫不夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 言行举止可别模仿我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你呢 别用手指着我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月 你对着镜子抱怨什么呢
